      "span_text": "We previously demonstrated that the ability of aha1 and aha2 knockdown mutants to grow normally was not due to compensation at the mRNA or protein level of other AHA members, as quantitative RNA and protein measurements did not show a significant increase in the concentration of mRNA or protein derived from any of the 10 other AHA genes  ."
